# Deploy2 — Maryland Driveway Restore

## Context
deploy.out confirmed full live deployment (bridge + GH Pages) with 20/20 Playwright tests passing. CEO build review (v4) identified one remaining gate-5 violation: en-dash (`&#8211;`) title separator from Rank Math default.

## Actions taken

### En-dash fix — functions.php on Surface Docker container

CEO finding: every page `<title>` used `&#8211;` (Rank Math default) — banned by gate #5.

Fix: appended WP filter to `/var/www/html/wp-content/themes/mdr-theme/functions.php` inside `mdr-wordpress` container via runner:
```php
add_filter('document_title_separator', function() { return '|'; });
```
WP-CLI confirmed separator resolves to `|`. Object cache flushed.

No git push needed (fix is on live Docker volume; container registered in services.json and auto-restarts with the fixed file).

---

