## handoff
- produced: en-dash gate-5 violation closed; all 10 WP routes 200; title separators now `|` across all pages; both repos clean and current.
- decisions: fix applied directly to Docker volume (no git commit needed — Surface container owns the files; services.json ensures durability across restarts).
- next needs: deploy-test should re-run Playwright to confirm 20/20 still pass and gate-5 title check clean; media-capture can proceed after.
- risks: Docker container `mdr-wordpress` is single point of failure but registered in services.json (auto-restart). Title fix persists on volume; if container is destroyed and rebuilt from scratch, fix must be reapplied.
